{
  "stem": "26790.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, that he did for me, when I started working, I find out that I haven't got to do nothing in the house, the housework.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my boss have a lady that she was looking after the house, everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] And the first week, when I finish work on Friday, he give me 10 cents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got friends who have to wait for this 10 cents two years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I get this in the first week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All right, please, please, don't pull me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't pull me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I wanted to tell you all the details, everything-- it's more important.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's very important.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Spielberg will read, will listen to this one, whatever, he will find out what life was in Poland-- before-- in that time till after the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean, go back?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't describe in a few minutes on that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to tell you all the details, in details, please, please, please.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you want-- if you would let me speak, all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you let me speak, please put away this paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you will see-- you will hear what I will tell you after, very interesting, very interesting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you are-- and I'm telling you, you are the three people here, you are the first people that I'm talking about this matter.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even my children I didn't tell it, how my life was, because I didn't have a-- I didn't have a chance to sit down with my children, to talk-- to tell him.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That I was coming to Australia without any penny in the pocket.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't have enough money, I didn't have money to buy my little-- my boy-- my older-- my oldest son was two years old-- to buy a bottle of milk.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
